item.title: How to change the teleports in normal books? [DELTA]
item.dc:creator: @xX_Energy_xX xX_Energy_xX
item.description:
@xX_Energy_xX wrote:

here’s the steps:

  1. open clicking most
  2. run your server and teleport to the one that you wanna change
  3. type ::mypos and search it on clicking most. (this may take a bit because the teleports when u first start are 3x3)
  4. go to clicking most, search the telport, once found change the x and y coords to the one that you want.
  5. compile

(heres what step 4 should look like)
c.triggerTele(3564, 3288, 0);
